description.en: The new work of the Turtle-footed writer prepared after a year and a half! H-mate Season 2!! After university is out, Tae Yong asks his brother, Tae-bong, to be the manager of his share house for a year to travel to the labyrinth. Taeyong's share house, which he was given permission for, was seen under the blue sky and the bright sunshine...Butt?!
